[9] Brazil (Rio de Janeiro)
Date: Sat 29 Mar 2008
Source: Globo.com [in Portuguese, trans. & summ. Mod.TY,edited]
<http://g1.globo.com/Noticias/Rio/0,,MUL374451-5606,00
MENINA+DE+ANOS+PODE+SER+A+VITIMA+DA+DENGUE.html>


A 7-year-old child may be the 55th dengue victim in Rio de Janeiro
state. The death occurred on Sat (29 Mar [2008]). The statistics,
updated by the state Secretariat of Health, indicated that up to the
present, there have been 54 deaths since the beginning of the
outbreak which began in mid-2007.

